headline: Jodi Rolland Joins U.S. Bank Wealth Management as President, Affluent Wealth Management
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 30, 2025--U.S. Bancorp announced that on Sept. 22, 2025, veteran wealth management leader Jodi Rolland joined the company as President, Affluent Wealth Management and will assume the role of CEO for U.S. Bancorp Investments (USBI) and U.S. Bancorp Advisors (USBA), with the effective date to be announced.
